<dl id="n11022b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11022b">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11022b"> 22(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ contumacity</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">&hellip; <b>Heavily Fined.</b> For his <mark>&ldquo;contumacity&rdquo;</mark> Finnerty was heavily fined, sentenced to two years&apos; imprisonment, and condemned to stand in the pillory which was at that time adjacent to the Green street Courthouse and Jail. <small> <a name="FJ23may24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#FJ23may24"><cite title="source">Freeman's Journal</cite></a> (23 May 1924) 8/4-5</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
